node.text: Those living with EB can teach us lessons in humility, grace, and bravery. It was an honor to get to know John Hudson and be a part of the #VentureintoCures Virtual Event last night. The world will be a better place when we #HealEB. I encourage you to donate and learn more about @ebresearch by going to ebresearch.org. This video was animated by @davefranciosaart & directed by @mattfinlin of Doorknocker Media. @eddievedder

node.text:
For the first time in 3000 years the Tasmania devils are back on mainland Australia! As top predators, the devils push back feral cats and foxes, allowing Australia’s native small mammals to recover so they can get to work enriching soil as they forage and help forests regenerate. My family and I were lucky enough to be there and lend a hand with the wonderful team at @wild.ark @aussieark @global_wildlife_conservation and #DevilComeback #ReWildAustralia
Head to devilcomeback.org to support!
Shot by visionary, genius ,majestic, Spaniard @cristianprieto.filmmaker

node.text: Tomorrow I am thrilled to be joining speakers, musicians and artists from 20 countries for @TEDCountdown — a free, global live streaming event on @YouTube! Visit the link in the bio to set an event reminder so you won’t miss a moment! #JoinTheCountdown

node.text: It was great to spend some time with #swissewellness and @the_malloys earlier this year talking about what it means to live a healthier, happier life. We discussed how training mindfully, eating well, and finding balance in good sleep and recovery have all had a snowball effect on other areas of my life.

node.text: Making this film was one of the most exhausting but rewarding experiences I’ve ever had on a set. Our director @thesamhargrave pushed the boundaries like no other. We set out to make the most insane, intense action film and I couldn’t be prouder of what we’ve achieved and beyond thankful to everyone involved in making this film possible. It releases tomorrow on @netflix - I can’t wait for you all to finally see it.

node.text: I’m very proud of all the hard work that has been poured into this project. Thank you @thesamhargrave @rudhrakshjaiswal1 @therussobrothers, and @netflixfilm for the opportunity to help bring this story to life.

node.text:
I’ve had a lot of questions about my prep and training for Thor over the years. This time round I I was fortunate enough to have a solid period at home to try a multitude of nutritional and training methods, to build the strongest version of myself and the character yet. From that I decided to design a fully guided program on how I achieved those results. Eat, train, sleep repeat! With our Centr Power program.
It launches June 21st @centrfit sign up now for your free trial 7 day trial at Centr.com #centrpower link in bio 🎥 @cristianprieto.filmmaker

node.text: Big announcement, @centrfit has won the @thefitsummit wellness award, APP OF THE YEAR 🎉 Huge thanks to all the team who have worked tirelessly to bring you the best health/fitness/wellness app in the game. Honoured to be a part of the journey and path with you all to build the best version of ourselves, healthier, happier, stronger!thanks to all the members and #centrfit family🙏🤙💪. Lotta love !

node.text: That’s a wrap on Thor Love and Thunder, it’s also national don’t flex day so I thought this super relaxed photo was appropriate. The film is gonna be batshit crazy off the wall funny and might also pull a heart string or two. Lots of love, lots of thunder! Thank you to all the cast and crew who made this another incredible Marvel journey. Buckle in, get ready and see ya in cinemas!! @taikawaititi @marvelstudios 📷 @jasinboland

node.text: “I’m sure like most people the biggest issue when wearing a suit is being unable to spontaneously launch yourself into a soccer challenge. Well rest assured those days are over. @boss now has suits that are so comfortable, stylish and full of stretch that basically you can now partake in any and all impromptu sporting events then head straight out to dinner in the same outfit! And don’t forget to spray #BOSSbottled! #SuitChallenge”

node.text:
Holding my little man’s hand and asking him the age old question. “What do you want to be when you grow up”
“Dad i wanna be Superman”  Lucky I have two other kids
